Create Terabox Account
- Terabox Account
- Login terabox.com
- Create Link

a. Terabox Account

	1. Open Chrome Browser, type "Terabox" and click on "terabox.com"
	2. click on "SIGN UP"
		
		- Enter your email : your email or signup by gmail
		- click on "Verify e-mail address"
		- open your email and copy mail code and paste in "Terabox" site
		- Enter your password:
		- Enter Confirm Password:
		- click on "Register Now" 

b. Login terabox.com

	1. Open Chrome Browser, type "Terabox" and click on "terabox.com"
	2. click on "Login"

c. Create Link
	
	- After login terabox.com, click on "Campaigns" --> Join Now 
	- in Video Plays, click on "Join This Plan"
	- agree, got it (click)
	- click on "Share Videos To Earn Money" 
	- click on "Add from desktop" --> Select files (select a video file)
	- click on "Generate Link" button
	- copy link
	 
	
		
